{"serial": "54010", "department_serial": 54, "code": "NL7047", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Interdisciplinary Design and Innovative Technology", "ch": "跨域設計與創新科技"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Ju-Ling Shih"], "ch": ["施如齡"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "E6", "room": "A406"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 30, "department": {"ch": "網路學習科技研究所碩士班", "en": "Graduate Institute of Network Learning Technology"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "部分英語", "en": "Partially English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 36, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "此課程主要以設計思考為基礎，輔以創新問題解決策略，帶領學生以理論為基礎，融合跨領域之系統概念、內容與方法，設計與發展各種教材教法、建構互動式教學環境，並討論創新科技應用與導入的機制。內容包括：系統科學、設計思考、創新策略、跨域教學設計、隱喻思考與創作、科技創新、研究與觀點等等。", "en": "The course will guide students to use design thinking and innovative problem-solving skills, integrate interdisciplinary systematic concepts, content, and methods, to design teaching strategies, develop learning materials, construct an interactive learning environment, and discuss innovative technology use and applications and related mechanisms. Content may include Systems Science, Design Thinking, Innovation Strategies, Interdisciplinary Instructional Design, Metaphoric Thinking and Creations, Technology Innovation, Research and Perspectives, etc."}, "outline": {"ch": "用專題導向、主題探討的方式進行。從傳統的教學設計課程的理論講授與教案設計晉級，從學習與教學的角度，一起來想想人類社會演進的幾個關鍵時期和特徵，以及其產生的相關課題。設計並開發科技導入課程，引導學生進行社會性科學議題的體驗與探討，提升學生思辨能力。", "en": "It is a theme-based project-oriented course which started from traditional instructional design with theoretical investigation. Students are led to do indepth discussions of human social evolution that generates socioscientific issues, and to develop innovative instructional design to guide young students to conduct scientific inquiry and issue discussion."}, "textbook": {"